#### Fadal Machining Centers v. Mid-Atlantic CNC (Jurisdictional Requirements)
Background: This case involves determining whether federal district court has diversity jurisdiction over a lawsuit between LLCs and corporations.

The relevant parties are:
- Fadal Machining Centers, LLC (Delaware LLC) - 10% owned by SP MAG Holdings (Delaware LLC with members including Silver Point Capital Fund and SPCP Group III).
- SP MAG Holdings (Delaware LLC)
- Silver Point Capital Fund (Delaware limited partnership)
- SPCP Group III (Delaware LLC)

The key member is Robert O’Shea, who is a New Jersey citizen.

:p Does the district court have diversity jurisdiction over Fadal Machining Centers v. Mid-Atlantic CNC?
