#### Delivery of Possession
Delivery of possession involves transferring control and exclusive custody of the property to the bailee. The bailee must knowingly accept the property and have sole control over it.

Example: When Delacroix checks her coat at a restaurant, but there is a diamond necklace in the pocket, only the coat forms a bailment because the restaurant accepts the coat with knowledge.
:p What does delivery of possession mean?
??x
Delivery of possession means transferring exclusive control and custody of personal property to another party (the bailee). The bailee must knowingly accept the property and have sole control over it.

